    Ready to work together?
</h2>
<p class="text-lg text-pretty mb-4">
        I'm currently looking for new opportunities. Whether you a question or just want to say hi, my inbox is ready and waiting!
    </p>

    <div class="flex flex-col justify-center md:flex-row gap-4">
        <SocialPill href="mailto:stephennicholasjones9@gmail.com" class="social-pill hover:ring-2 hover:ring-white/50 px-3 md:px-6">
            <Gmail class="size-5 md:size-6" />
            <span>Drop me a line!</span>
        </SocialPill>

        <SocialPill href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/stephen-nicholas-jones-de-giorgi-50668449/" class="social-pill px-3 md:px-6">
